{"tid":277646,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【鬼國】廣東800多個罪犯被判刑後 一直沒有執行刑罰　制度混亂及貪污","createTime":"2017-06-09T18:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T21:40:50.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"278f2e8032d94f5b1b1de9ea625ac3bec0d02177","tid":277646,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T18:51:39.000Z","msg":"有線新聞 i-Cable News<br />\n1 hr &middot;<br />\n【逾八百犯判刑後不翼而飛】<br />\n【律師: 靠關係逃過制裁】<br />\n<br />\n廣東負責監督各級檢察院工作的刑事執行檢察部門發現，過去一年來在執行犯人刑罰工作上相當粗疏。<br />\n<br />\n有 800 多個罪犯雖然已經被判刑，但一直沒有執行刑罰。當中包括一個被判死緩、兩個被判無期徒刑和 33 個判十年以上有期徒刑的重犯。<br />\n<br />\n檢察部門稱，沒有收監的罪犯中，其中超過 280 人已經下落不明。<br />\n<br />\n有律師認為，主要問題出於制度上的混亂及貪污所致。<br />\n<br />\n「羈押和囚禁犯人，主要由公安部門負責，當中牽涉錯綜複雜的利益和人事關係，並不是單單檢察部門能解決的問題。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/688001328058605/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F688001328058605%2F&d=EJSBKswcsDeyrrrmgNYb6U4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=b4eb5f13\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/688001328058605/</a>"},{"pid":"9b41cbab72164178b10589b1492096fc82185183","tid":277646,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T20:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e951f168dd2eeb3735d6f16fc592a21733a4e2e","tid":277646,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T20:43:08.000Z","msg":"「羈押和囚禁犯人，主要由公安部門負責，當中牽涉錯綜複雜的利益和人事關係，並不是單單檢察部門能解決的問題。」<br />\n<br />\n佢講晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n檢察部門本身應該防止同取締呢啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b2a39ed5ec6c85f08f1725ec7c8af1a06d9859","tid":277646,"uid":22869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T21:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.giphy.com/xUA7b4sW6QJn3tdyWA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt